if exists(select 1 from sys.sysforeignkey where role='FK_MPS_NASE_ADMINSTRA_MPS_OPST') then
alter table MPS_NASELJENO_MESTO
delete foreign key FK_MPS_NASE_ADMINSTRA_MPS_OPST
end if;

alter table MPS_NASELJENO_MESTO
add constraint FK_MPS_NASE_ADMINSTRA_MPS_OPST foreign key (MPS_DR_IDENTIFIKATOR, OP_OZNAKA)
references MPS_OPSTINA (DR_IDENTIFIKATOR, OP_OZNAKA)
on update restrict
on delete restrict;
